{
  "stem": "21611.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that-- and we were in those bunkers in the cold, in the dampness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were lying one-- one next to the other, to keep us warm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't-- you know, I can't even think now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did I have?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Ukrainian, they have from wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how you call them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We called them [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how you call them in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wood.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They make, from wood, shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Wood shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Winter was very bad because the Ukrainian could find us very easy because of the snow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could trace us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the summer was easier because they put grass on the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they couldn't-- they made such a wonders, I'm telling you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't even see there are people hiding inside in this-- in this darkness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to think we'll survive another hour, another minute, and we'll be killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what we spend our time thinking, and praying only to be shot, not to be tortured.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were so frightened and so much fear, always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Always very bad palpitations, scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a terrible thing, fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You want to live, and you know you'll die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, some of them, they-- they left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I buried a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With my hands I buried with them, with shovels, because they were killed and they weren't buried.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the only parts, the remains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I think about it, how I could do it, I still it's a mystery to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I don't think I'll ever find that out how I did it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Couldn't cry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no tears in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Couldn't cry.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
